Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
Book The Book class represents exchange books.
ExchangeManager The ExchangeManager class implements the whole process when received an order, including execute order and add order if necessary.
NewOrderImpl The NewOrderImpl class implements NewOrder Interface, it represents a new order.
OrderCxRImpl The OrderCxRImpl class implements OrderCxR Interface, it represents a cancel or replace order.
Runner The Runner class used to simulate the exchange process and print the process and final state of the book.
SilentRunner The SilentRunner class used to simulate the exchange process and not print the process, but print final state of the book.
 

Enum Summary
BookType The BookType class includes type of a book: ASK <--> BID
